Customer: 38203.

Executive: Surekhanand. Aur Surekha mam.

Executive: Sir ek din hum waha kab gaye kal gaye kyu gaye?

Customer: Aap khud catalog dekho. Hmm. Aur mere ko bata do galat kiska hai.
Executive: Thik hai main inko ye number de deti hu aur ye aapke staff se baat kar lengi aur main karwa leti hu ki kitne product aur bache hain add hone ko ye batao.
Customer: 60 product add hue hai dekho aap dekho na mere ko madam main aapko hai sir main hai na suno na main aapko hai na mera personal number se mere ko ek ring karwati aur hi dalo main uske upar mera details bhej deta hu kitna product hai.
Executive: Nahi maine khol ke rakha hai sir uski jarurat nahi hai 82 product aapke add hai abhi.

Customer: Madam isme kya hota hai dekho aap aapke hisab se barabar baat kar rahi ho lekin jo system manta hai na system ke hisab se kam nahi chal raha hai wo thoda unko bolo system ke hisab se kam karo.
Executive: Chalo main inko call karke bol deti hu to sir main fir yahan se aapka concern ye close kar du unko call karke main aapko.
Customer: Nahi concern turant mat close karo khatam karo pahla jab tak khatam nahi ho jayega na pura mera tab tak concern mat close karo.
Executive: To sir concern on rehne se bhi koi matlab thodi hai.
Customer: Nahi hai hai matlab hai na usko nahi hota to nahi hota to call nahi aata wo jante humko koi baat nahi karne ka humne paisa diya hai uska pure pure humko reason mangta hai hamara product list barabar karo humne jo diya hai aapko usme se clear karo aur aaj ke aaj khatam karo fir concern close karo.
Executive: Thik hai main baat karti hu kitna time aur lag raha hai.
Customer: Haan thik hai.
